  <brief_title>Relation Between Withdrawal Movement for Rocuronium and Emergence Agitation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Relation Between Withdrawal Movement on Rocuronium Injection and Emergence Agitation and Pain in Preschool Ages: Observational Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
